#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Cauchy Product of Species of Types]

Let $F: Uu_1 -> Uu_2$ and $G : Uu_1 -> Uu_3$ be #local("008K")[species of types]. We define the _cauchy product_ of $F$ and $G$ on $X :Uu$ as
$
(S * T)(X) := Sigma_(k, l : Uu_1) Sigma_(e : k+l ~= X) F(k) xx F(l).
$

